abstract: Yani Tseng wins LPGA Hana Bank Championship; other golf results noted.
snippet: Top-ranked Yani Tseng won the L.P.G.A. Hana Bank Championship in Incheon, South Korea, for her sixth victory on the tour this season and ninth over all.
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Yani Tseng won the L.P.G.A. Hana Bank Championship in Incheon, South Korea, for her sixth victory on the tour this season and ninth over all.

headline.main: Tseng Wins Sixth Title of Year
headline.print_headline: Tseng Wins Sixth Title of Year
